OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FImran Khan's sons have accused the
OL,8,FPakistani government of using the Iran
OL,9,Fpeace talks to divert away from the
OL,10,Ftreatment of their father
OL,12,FThe sons of Pakistan's jailed former
OL,13,Fprime minister Imran Khan have accused
OL,14,Fthe country's government of using the
OL,15,FIran peace talks to burnish its
OL,16,Finternational image, diverting
OL,17,Fattention from his "inhumane"
OL,18,Ftreatment after almost 1,000 days in
OL,19,Fdetention.
OL,26,@yD@TOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FKasim and Sulaiman Khan told ITV News
OL,8,Ftheir father called off protests
OL,9,Fduring recent Iran peace talks in
OL,10,FIslamabad to avoid a "bloodbath"
OL,11,Fdisrupting negotiations, despite
OL,12,Fmounting concern over his condition -
OL,13,Fthey say he has lost most of his
OL,14,Fvision in one eye after being denied
OL,15,Fproper medical care.
OL,17,F"Only as recently as during the peace
OL,18,Ftalks in Islamabad, our father
OL,19,Factually got to meet his lawyer,
OL,20,Ffinally - the first time in months",
OL,21,FSulaiman, his eldest son, revealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"He decided to call off a protest that
OL,8,Fhis party were going to hold during
OL,9,Fthe peace talks, because he cares
OL,10,Fultimately about the image of his
OL,11,Fcountry - and for peace in the Middle
OL,12,FEast.
OL,14,F"He thought that that was more
OL,15,Fimportant than his own situation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FImran Khan decided against "causing
OL,8,Fchaos", Kasim said. "The Pakistani
OL,9,Farmy would come out in force and
OL,10,Fthey'd open fire, they have in the
OL,11,Fpast for a protest in Pakistan for his
OL,12,Frelease."
OL,14,FSoldiers and police officers were
OL,15,Faccused of firing on civilians in
OL,16,FNovember 2024, resulting in multiple
OL,17,Fdeaths and injuries, when protestors
OL,18,Fmarched to Islamabad demanding Khan's
OL,19,Frelease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"They've done it multiple times in the
OL,8,Fpast and they're a very powerful army
OL,9,Fwho won't roll over unless for
OL,10,Fanything, (except) maybe the
OL,11,Fsuperpowers, or global superpowers
OL,12,Flike America who, what they've done
OL,13,Finstead, is opted to become a puppet
OL,14,Fgovernment that essentially offered
OL,15,FTrump the Nobel Peace Prize, crypto
OL,16,Fcurrencies, natural minerals,
OL,17,Fabsolutely anything they can to claw
OL,18,Ftheir way into his good books."
OL,26,@rD@KpmrD@Rpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
