PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FSulaiman agreed: "I think the
OL,8,FPakistani regime are doing their best
OL,9,Fto clean up their image on the
OL,10,Finternational stage.
OL,12,F"It does seem like it's working at the
OL,13,Fmoment. They presented themselves as
OL,14,Fkind of peace brokers."
OL,16,FImran Khan, the former World Cup-
OL,17,Fwinning cricket captain of Pakistan,
OL,18,Fturned politician, was imprisoned in
OL,19,FAugust 2023 and has faced 100 charges.
OL,20,FHe is being detained in solitary
OL,21,Fconfinement.
OL,26,@vD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
