PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FKhan denies all charges against him,
OL,8,Fclaiming they are politically
OL,9,Fmotivated. He is made to spend up to
OL,10,F23 hours a day in his prison cell, his
OL,11,Ffamily say, and is granted only
OL,12,Foccasional phone calls with family
OL,13,Fmembers.
OL,15,FFor his sons in London, those calls
OL,16,Fhave fallen silent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FThe last time they heard his voice was
OL,8,Ffour weeks ago, on a Saturday morning
OL,9,Fjust after Eid, when an unexpected
OL,10,Fcall came through from an unknown
OL,11,FPakistani number.
OL,13,F"Kasim picked it up and quickly got me
OL,14,Fto get to the phone," said Sulaiman.
OL,16,F"He spoke to someone who said, 'Your
OL,17,Ffather's on the line - can you be on
OL,18,Fthe phone in the next 10 minutes?' And
OL,19,Fluckily, he got me in time and we both
OL,20,Fmanaged to get on the phone with our
OL,21,Ffather."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"But it's all so slapdash, the whole
OL,8,Fprocess", Kasim added. "If we don't
OL,9,Fget it right, which has happened in
OL,10,Fthe past, we don't get to speak to him
OL,11,F- and then it's another three, four
OL,12,Fmonths."
OL,14,FDuring the twenty-minute conversation
OL,15,Fwith his sons, Khan shared updates
OL,16,Fabout his health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"This time, he was definitely the most
OL,8,Ffrustrated out of some of the times
OL,9,Fwe've spoken to him", Kasim said,
OL,10,Fdescribing his father's mood on the
OL,11,Fcall, "it was a lot to do with the
OL,12,Fsituation with his eye".
OL,14,F"They're just doing the very bare
OL,15,Fminimum with the treatment of his eye
OL,16,Fbecause they're not taking him to a
OL,17,Fdoctor, to a hospital."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FSulaiman added, "he said he's lost
OL,8,Fabout 80, 85% vision in his right eye
OL,9,Fand he doesn't think that it will ever
OL,10,Fget back to normal".
OL,12,FReports of his deteriorating health
OL,13,Fecho those of his wife's condition.
OL,15,FBushra Bibi, also jailed on corruption
OL,16,Fcharges she denies, was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital this week after reporting
OL,18,Fimpaired vision ` raising concerns she
OL,19,Ftoo is losing her sight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
