PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHer supporters say her health has
OL,13,F"deteriorated significantly". She was
OL,14,Fswiftly returned to her cell,
OL,15,Faccording to supporters ` part of what
OL,16,Fthey call a campaign to "push Imran
OL,17,FKhan to the edge".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@\O]xD@YOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"What is perhaps most disturbing is
OL,8,Fthat, even with stitches in her eye,
OL,9,Fshe was not allowed to remain in the
OL,10,Fhospital for even a couple of days
OL,11,Fafter surgery, despite being in
OL,12,Fimmense pain... a basic right for any
OL,13,Fpatient", said Zulfi Bukhari, a senior
OL,14,Fadvisor to Mr Khan who is accompanying
OL,15,Fthe brothers on their campaign to
OL,16,Fraise awareness of their father's case.
OL,18,FAnd speaking of his father's
OL,19,Fconditions in detention, Sulaiman Khan
OL,20,Ftold ITV News: "He's not allowed any
OL,21,Fbooks in prison".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FA small concession, recently secured
OL,8,Fby his lawyers and described by Kasim
OL,9,Fas a "win", was access to a daily
OL,10,Fnewspaper, delivered to his cramped
OL,11,Fcell - a thin connection to the
OL,12,Foutside world.
OL,14,F"I think it was about random celebrity
OL,15,Fobituaries and things like that, which
OL,16,Fisn't exactly his usual reading
OL,17,Fmaterial, but he said it's better than
OL,18,Fnothing."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776607870
OL,3,C'We're desperate': Sons of jailed
OL,4,CImran Khan criticise Pakistan's
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FLast month, the brothers called on the
OL,8,FUnited Nations to intervene to end
OL,9,Fwhat they and other experts believe is
OL,10,Fthe "arbitrary detention" and
OL,11,F"torture" of their father.
OL,13,F"We've gone from pushing for him to be
OL,14,Freleased, for pushing for him to get a
OL,15,Ffree and fair trial to now - just
OL,16,Fhoping that he gets the bare
OL,17,Fnecessities.
OL,19,F"It's frustrating for us to have to
OL,20,Frelegate our ambitions, but at this
OL,21,Fpoint we're quite desperate."
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@YO]sD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
